%% Diagram: HTML parsing pipeline — bytes through tokenizer + tree construction to DOM, with preload scanner running in parallel
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    Bytes["HTML bytes\n(stream)"]
    Tok["Tokenizer\n80+ states\n6 token types"]
    Tree["Tree construction\n23 insertion modes\n+ error recovery"]
    DOM["DOM tree"]
    PS["Preload scanner\n(off-thread)"]

    Bytes --> Tok --> Tree --> DOM
    Bytes -. "scan ahead\nlink/script/img" .-> PS
